{"title":"","uid":"f73a8e23e6f6f669cf99c7dba8fa0722","slug":"GAME_DEV/2DGAME","date":"2023-03-07T16:14:45.050Z","updated":"2022-12-10T11:31:31.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/GAME_DEV/2DGAME.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"STAGE-1-Project-Setup\"><a href=\"#STAGE-1-Project-Setup\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"STAGE 1: Project Setup\"></a>STAGE 1: Project Setup</h2><ul>\n<li><p>Create a 2D URP Project</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Set Preset for Textures</p>\n<ul>\n<li>16px * 16px grid</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Apply preset manually to all existing pixel art</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"STAGE-2-Install-Art-Packs\"><a href=\"#STAGE-2-Install-Art-Packs\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"STAGE 2: Install Art Packs\"></a>STAGE 2: Install Art Packs</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://rvros.itch.io/animated-pixel-hero\">Animated Pixel Adventurer by rvros (itch.io)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://aamatniekss.itch.io/fantasy-knight-free-pixelart-animated-character\">Fantasy Knight - Free Pixelart Animated Character by aamatniekss (itch.io)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://managore.itch.io/m5x7\">https://managore.itch.io/m5x7</a> Typeface / Font</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://aamatniekss.itch.io/free-pixelart-tileset-cute-forest\">https://aamatniekss.itch.io/free-pixelart-tileset-cute-forest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://henrysoftware.itch.io/pixel-food\">https://henrysoftware.itch.io/pixel-food</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://kyrise.itch.io/kyrises-free-16x16-rpg-icon-pack\">Kyrise’s Free 16x16 RPG Icon Pack by Kyrise (itch.io)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://luizmelo.itch.io/monsters-creatures-fantasy\">Monsters Creatures Fantasy by LuizMelo (itch.io)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youfulca.itch.io/legendary-jrpg-battle-music-pack\">Legendary JRPG Battle Music Pack FREE by YouFulca (itch.io)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://leohpaz.itch.io/rpg-essentials-sfx-free\">RPG Essentials SFX - Free! by Leohpaz (itch.io)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"STAGE-3-Install-Necessary-Unity-Packages\"><a href=\"#STAGE-3-Install-Necessary-Unity-Packages\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"STAGE 3: Install Necessary Unity Packages\"></a>STAGE 3: Install Necessary Unity Packages</h2><ul>\n<li>Intsall “Cinemachine” </li>\n<li>Install “Input System”</li>\n<li><del>Change Project Setting: Turn off Reload Domain(faster loading of scenes in editor)</del>(may cause some potential errors)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"STAGE-4-Create-Background\"><a href=\"#STAGE-4-Create-Background\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"STAGE 4: Create Background\"></a>STAGE 4: Create Background</h2><ul>\n<li>创建背景: sprite renderer</li>\n<li>设定sorting layer</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Layer、Sorting Layer and Order in Layer</p>\n<h2 id=\"STAGE-5-Setup-player-basic-move-left-and-right\"><a href=\"#STAGE-5-Setup-player-basic-move-left-and-right\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"STAGE 5: Setup player(basic move: left and right)\"></a>STAGE 5: Setup player(basic move: left and right)</h2><ul>\n<li>SpriteRenderer</li>\n<li>Rigidbody2D: diff with “rigidbody”</li>\n<li>prefabs: make and change</li>\n<li>Player Input Component: with assert needed</li>\n<li>PlayerController script movement: start to write the control script</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"r